'''Steng's Talons''' were a melee weapon used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Made from [[sgauru]] [[Bone/Legends|bones]] and covered with [[yorik coral]], the talons were inserted into the body of a [[Warrior caste|warrior]] who had proved himself in battle. They could be extended or contracted by a muscle movement. The placing of the talons was very dangerous, and few warriors actually survived the [[escalation]]. Those who did received even greater honor. The talons were included as part of the arsenal of the elite [[Slayers]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

Steng's talons take their name from [[Steng]], the first of the [[warmaster]]s.<ref name="TUF" />

